{"tid":480504,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"《坤輿萬國全圖》是明代萬曆年間繪製的世界地圖","createTime":"2017-11-26T08:29:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-28T14:00:07.000Z","uid":51701,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"5a9fbbc5121e6c851fa07ec7d3021ca2c322b53c","tid":480504,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T08:29:07.000Z","msg":"《坤輿萬國全圖》是明代萬曆年間繪製的世界地圖，在地理學和製圖學界具有重要位置。經多次翻印摹抄，影響深遠。西方人士稱其為「不可能的黑鬱金香」。[1]天主教耶穌會傳教士利瑪竇參與繪製。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n簡介[編輯]<br />\n<br />\n傳入日本並經抄繪、上色的「坤輿萬國全圖」<br />\n《坤輿萬國全圖》高5英尺（1.52米），寬12英尺（3.66米），該圖<ins><strong><strong>並非以中國為中心</strong></strong></ins>，中國位於地圖中間線偏左的地方。<br />\n亞細亞（亞洲）<br />\n歐羅巴（歐洲）<br />\n利未亞（非洲）<br />\n南北亞墨利加（南北美洲）<br />\n墨瓦蠟泥加（南極洲與澳大利亞）<br />\n附註地理誌異，繪有風俗禽獸；四方各置「九重天圖」、「天地儀圖」、「日月食圖」、「中氣圖」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現存[編輯]<br />\n目前已發現的《坤輿萬國全圖》原刻本有六幅，其中保存狀況較好的有2幅，這兩幅現藏於梵蒂岡宗座圖書館，和美國明尼蘇達大學的詹姆斯&middot;福特&middot;貝爾圖書館[1]。剩餘四幅現藏於日本京都大學、日本宮城縣圖書館、日本內閣圖書館和法國巴黎的私人收藏中。<br />\n<ins><em><strong>目前中國沒有《坤輿萬國全圖》原刻本的收藏。</strong></em></ins>中國國內現存最早的、也是唯一的，據刻本摹繪的彩色《坤輿萬國全圖》現藏於南京博物院[2]。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/71/Kunyu_Wanguo_Quantu_%28坤輿萬國全圖%29.jpg/505px-Kunyu_Wanguo_Quantu_%28坤輿萬國全圖%29.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fthumb%2F7%2F71%2FKunyu_Wanguo_Quantu_%2528%E5%9D%A4%E8%BC%BF%E8%90%AC%E5%9C%8B%E5%85%A8%E5%9C%96%2529.jpg%2F505px-Kunyu_Wanguo_Quantu_%2528%E5%9D%A4%E8%BC%BF%E8%90%AC%E5%9C%8B%E5%85%A8%E5%9C%96%2529.jpg&h=a6508a3b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n清朝班垃圾自卑到自大<br />\n成日ＦＦ萬國來朝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同而家班支那有咩分別"},{"pid":"812c00525dbcd730fc5c0f26aa3764fb51373e32","tid":480504,"uid":87780,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T06:12:16.000Z","msg":"冇大洋洲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34623d791f25b962a2a7e7b233626bfc75127899","tid":480504,"uid":104443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T07:40:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇大洋洲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n地圖應該當左南極係大洋州<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37c27ae8ddbde27a3f15f99ed826d819b6c5994b","tid":480504,"uid":100150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T08:26:02.000Z","msg":"留名<br />\n大明帝國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n比起瀛寰志略仲要早幾百年"},{"pid":"5684b318e2bc8da4432a66854108680bea2df591","tid":480504,"uid":50327,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T08:28:52.000Z","msg":"當年西方人已經sm緊美洲人<br />\n明朝人仲係度井內玩泥沙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5a77d712227bb87a6fae654c92d598286af8522","tid":480504,"uid":522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T08:31:37.000Z","msg":"除左目測仲有咩方法可以製作咁仔細既世界地圖"},{"pid":"2e2c1f56fd9d67322a0ca193c1f58170457f9dc1","tid":480504,"uid":100150,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T08:32:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>除左目測仲有咩方法可以製作咁仔細既世界地圖</blockquote><br />\n傳教士"},{"pid":"26071e5c5f42779999996a8c1b4d98b38b0165ca","tid":480504,"uid":45657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T08:34:25.000Z","msg":"無衛星都畫到咁準真係好勁"},{"pid":"26f6be83d6cc3f8578ac6600f65e9a82651247bb","tid":480504,"uid":41846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T08:37:22.000Z","msg":"都有七八成似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好堅 冇科技都做到咁"},{"pid":"c147cd22aacd4e3f16ef56502ed691c0b2e5a9a6","tid":480504,"uid":41846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T08:37:22.000Z","msg":"都有七八成似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\"